            <span class="font-semibold">Secondo le loro leggi il colpevole...</span>
            <span class="text-green-600">‚Üí</span>
            <span>...doveva ripagare la vittima con dei beni.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center text-sm">6</span>
            <span class="font-semibold">La fine del regno degli Ittiti avvenne intorno al...</span>
            <span class="text-green-600">‚Üí</span>
            <span>...1200 a.C., per l'invasione di altri popoli.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Action buttons for exercise 2 -->
      <div class="mt-6 flex justify-center gap-4">
        <button data-action="click->sentence-matcher#checkAnswers"
                class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-green-600 hover:from-green-600 hover:to-green-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg transition transform hover:scale-105">
          ‚úì Verifica
        </button>
        <button data-action="click->sentence-matcher#reset"
                class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-500 to-gray-600 hover:from-gray-600 hover:to-gray-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg transition transform hover:scale-105">
          üîÑ Ricomincia
        </button>
        <button onclick="toggleSolutions2()"
                class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-blue-600 hover:from-blue-600 hover:to-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg transition transform hover:scale-105">
          üëÅÔ∏è Mostra Soluzioni
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Exercise Controls -->
    <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls', color: 'yellow', current_page: 'nvi4_sto_p155' %>

  </div>
</div>

<script>
  function toggleSolutions() {
    const solutions = document.querySelectorAll('.solution-box');
    solutions.forEach(solution => {
      solution.classList.toggle('hidden');
    });
  }

  function toggleSolutions2() {
    const solutions = document.querySelectorAll('.solution-box-2');
    solutions.forEach(solution => {
      solution.classList.toggle('hidden');
    });
  }
</script>

